OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FA Royal visitor has been enjoying warm
OL,7,Fweather and undertook a Crown first
OL,8,Fduring her two-day visit to Jersey
OL,9,Fthis week.
OL,11,FSophie, the Duchess of Edinburgh, has
OL,12,Fbeen making her way around Jersey
OL,13,Ffarms and also took to the English
OL,14,FChannel to visit a group of islands
OL,15,Fknown as the Ecrehous.
OL,17,FDespite it being Crown land, it is
OL,18,Fbelieved that no member of the Royal
OL,19,Ffamily has ever set foot on the
OL,20,Fislands.
OL,26,@wD@Qrr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
