FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782411505
OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FWhile there are no permanent residents
OL,7,Fliving there, representatives of the
OL,8,Farchipelago say it is a landmark
OL,9,Fmoment, which reaffirms the area as
OL,10,Fpart of the Bailiwick of Jersey.
OL,12,FThe Duchess started her day at Trinity
OL,13,FManor Farm.
OL,15,FThere, she was greeted by Jersey
OL,16,Fcattle and heard about the farm's
OL,17,Fsustainability efforts.
OL,19,FShe was specially introduced to a five-
OL,20,Fday-old calf, Louise, by a student
OL,21,Ffrom Beaulieu Convent School.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782411505
OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FThe Royal also received a briefing on
OL,7,Fhow Trinity Farm grows its own feed
OL,8,Fand bedding.
OL,10,FNext, the Duchess relocated to Peacock
OL,11,FFarm to meet with the Jersey Royal
OL,12,FCompany and hear about the work they
OL,13,Fdo to keep their farming
OL,14,Fenvironmentally responsible.
OL,16,FAfter a series of speeches, the Royal
OL,17,Frolled up her sleeves and helped out
OL,18,FSt Martin Primary School children to
OL,19,Fharvest some potatoes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782411505
OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FTwo students described it as an
OL,7,F"amazing, exciting" experience, with
OL,8,Fone girl saying: "Not every child gets
OL,9,Fto see the Duchess of Edinburgh!"
OL,11,FProceedings then moved from land to
OL,12,Fsea as the Royal party moved to St
OL,13,FCatherine's Breakwater.
OL,15,FThere, the Duchess met with young
OL,16,Fpeople preparing dishes with Jersey
OL,17,Fproduce before moving to the slipway.
OL,19,FThe team from Marine Resources and
OL,20,FManagement also had the chance to
OL,21,Fdiscuss their seabed survey work.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782411505
OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FThe Duchess then went aboard a fishing
OL,7,Ftrawler and watched as a pot full of
OL,8,Flobsters and crabs was raised from the
OL,9,Fsea.
OL,11,FIt was again another showcase of
OL,12,FJersey's produce and sustainable
OL,13,Fpractices.
OL,15,FThe day culminated in a visit to Les
OL,16,FEcrehous: a group of islands 10
OL,17,Fkilometres off the coast of St Martin.
OL,19,FThere, the Royal standard was raised
OL,20,Fon a specially erected flagpole.
OL,26,@xD@Drr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
