OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782411505
OL,3,CDuchess becomes first Royal to visit
OL,4,CJersey islands: In Pictures
OL,6,FThe Duchess also unveiled a plaque to
OL,7,Fcommemorate the visit and explored the
OL,8,Fislands before returning to Jersey.
OL,10,FAfter a long day of travel, she was
OL,11,Fable to enjoy an evening reception at
OL,12,FGovernment House with Jersey's
OL,13,FLieutenant-Governor.
OL,15,FThe Royal also met representatives
OL,16,Ffrom the NSPCC and other island
OL,17,Fcharities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
